OL,5, A key intelligence database used by    
OL,6, police to investigate extremists was   
OL,7, "not fit for purpose" when introduced  
OL,8, in 2014, a former counter-terrorism    
OL,9, officer has told the BBC.              
OL,11,FThe officer, who retired in 2018, says 
OL,12,Fthe National Common Intelligence       
OL,13,FApplication (NCIA) had serious flaws.  
OL,15,FCounter Terrorism Policing says        
OL,16,F"substantial improvements" were made   
OL,17,Ffollowing a significant review after   
OL,18,Fterror attacks in 2017, including at   
OL,19,Fthe Manchester Arena.                  
